rows.label: qst106001_0010
rows.name:
Dad, what's wrong, Mo-mo?
Does your tummy hurt, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0020
rows.name: Hmm? ...Ah, it's Tora, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0030
rows.name: My stomach isn't upset or anything, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0040
rows.name:
Masterpon always has good
meals, good sleep, and good
bowel movements, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0050
rows.name: Yes, yes, I'm in excellent health, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0060
rows.name:
That information is completely
unnecessary, mo. ...So, what
were you mumbling about, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0070
rows.name: Ah, well... Thing is...

rows.label: qst106001_0080
rows.name:
I was thinking about a
new mode for Hana, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0090
rows.name: Oh! Tora and Dad have same idea!

rows.label: qst106001_0100
rows.name:
Actually, Tora was also thinking
about powering up Hana soon, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0110
rows.name: What? Tora think that too?

rows.label: qst106001_0120
rows.name:
As expected of my son,
we think alike, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0130
rows.name:
So, what kind of mode was
Dad thinking about, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0140
rows.name:
Are you curious, Mo-mo?
Can't be helped, meh. I'll
specially show you, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0150
rows.name: This is Hana's final mode, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0160
rows.name: W-what's this?!

rows.label: qst106001_0170
rows.name:
What do you think, Mo-mo?
Are you speechless from how
amazing it is, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0180
rows.name: This mode called 'Super Fighter Mode'!

rows.label: qst106001_0190
rows.name:
This Hana size of ten Kiku.
More battle power than
Divine Beast warship.

rows.label: qst106001_0200
rows.name: What Dad thinking?!

rows.label: qst106001_0210
rows.name:
Dad just take old Hana
blueprint and enlarge!

rows.label: qst106001_0220
rows.name: Dad thinking just like Bahn...

rows.label: qst106001_0230
rows.name:
What, does Tora dislike
big things, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0240
rows.name: Then how about this, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0250
rows.name:
Uh? Hmmm... Too small
for Tora's eyesight...

rows.label: qst106001_0260
rows.name:
This is Hana compacted down to
an extremely small size, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0270
rows.name:
What do you mean 'extremely small
size', Mo-mo? Isn't this just a
reduced copy of the blueprint, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0280
rows.name:
First of all, if it's this small,
it won't be of any use, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0290
rows.name:
No, no, if it's the size of an ant,
it could infiltrate any place.

rows.label: qst106001_0300
rows.name:
And its power is the same as
before. This is truly an anâ€”

rows.label: qst106001_0310
rows.name:
Dad... Let's stop here because
going further would be problematic
in various ways, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0320
rows.name: Hmm... This is no good either, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0330
rows.name:
Just what kind of thing
does Tora prefer, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0340
rows.name:
Want to know, Mo-mo?
Want to know, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0350
rows.name: Can't be helped. I'll tell you, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0360
rows.name:
What Tora is thinking of
is... I call it JD Mode.

rows.label: qst106001_0370
rows.name: Jay-dee mode?

rows.label: qst106001_0380
rows.name: That's right, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0390
rows.name:
This time, Hana will aim
to be an even more adult
and mature woman, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0400
rows.name: Tora and Hana grow up together!

rows.label: qst106001_0410
rows.name:
Hmm... I don't know what
JD stands for, but...

rows.label: qst106001_0420
rows.name:
But Tora's extraordinary enthusiasm
is definitely coming across, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0430
rows.name: Dad! Dad like it!

rows.label: qst106001_0440
rows.name: Ah, I understand, mo. My son.

rows.label: qst106001_0450
rows.name:
Very well! Dad will get right
to it! Kiku! Ready my things!

rows.label: qst106001_0460
rows.name: Yes, Masterpon! At once.

rows.label: qst106001_0470
rows.name: Listen up, Hana.

rows.label: qst106001_0480
rows.name:
Tora and Dad will be holed up
in the back room for a while.

rows.label: qst106001_0490
rows.name:
Don't let anyone disturb very very
very important work! Got it?

rows.label: qst106001_0500
rows.name: Yes, Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106001_0510
rows.name: What is Tora planning to start?

rows.label: qst106001_0520
rows.name: Who knows...

rows.label: qst106001_0530
rows.name:
I heard something about
powering up Hana-chan.

rows.label: qst106001_0540
rows.name:
Something about being adult
and mature, like saying
"my head pain hurts."

rows.label: qst106001_0550
rows.name: You're not one to talk about others.

rows.label: qst106001_0560
rows.name: Huh? Why?

rows.label: qst106001_0570
rows.name: Wow, this guy doesn't even realize.

rows.label: qst106001_0580
rows.name:
If it's about powering
up, does that mean they're
going to modify Hana?

rows.label: qst106001_0590
rows.name: Guess so.

rows.label: qst106001_0600
rows.name:
But from the looks of it, they
probably won't come out for a while.

rows.label: qst106001_0610
rows.name:
Can't be helped. Let's go back
to the inn and take a rest.

rows.label: qst106001_0620
rows.name: Huh? They're still at it?

rows.label: qst106001_0630
rows.name: Yes.

rows.label: qst106001_0640
rows.name:
They've been going nonstop since
yesterday, without eating a single
meal or getting any sleep.

rows.label: qst106001_0650
rows.name:
Tora... He doesn't know what's
good for him, sometimes.

rows.label: qst106001_0660
rows.name:
If they don't moderate themselves,
they're going to collapse.

rows.label: qst106001_0670
rows.name: Urk!

rows.label: qst106001_0680
rows.name: My lady!

rows.label: qst106001_0690
rows.name: It's done! Finally completed!

rows.label: qst106001_0700
rows.name:
"Completed"...? Tora, just
what did you complete?

rows.label: qst106001_0710
rows.name: Mo-mo-mo...

rows.label: qst106001_0720
rows.name: Behold! Really something, huh?

rows.label: qst106001_0730
rows.name: Ooh!

rows.label: qst106001_0740
rows.name: This is! Hana's final form, mo!

rows.label: qst106001_0750
rows.name: M-my lady, get a hold of yourself!

rows.label: qst106001_0760
rows.name: ...gyagh...

rows.label: qst106001_0770
rows.name: T-Tora, Is this really okay?

rows.label: qst106001_0780
rows.name:
That might be a bit too adult
and too early for children.

rows.label: qst106001_0790
rows.name: Tora not care!

rows.label: qst106001_0800
rows.name:
Tora has made the decision to climb
the stairs to adulthood, mo.

rows.label: qst106001_0810
rows.name:
I see... You're so determined
to do this, Mo-mo?

rows.label: qst106001_0820
rows.name: Dad. Tora mean what he say.

rows.label: qst106001_0830
rows.name:
A real grown man stakes
his life on his dreams!

rows.label: qst106001_0840
rows.name: Well said, my son.

rows.label: qst106001_0850
rows.name: [ML:undisp ] AD LIB unease

rows.label: qst106001_0860
rows.name: Urgh...

rows.label: qst106001_0870
rows.name: Enough already... Get out of the way!!

rows.label: qst106001_0880
rows.name: Mo-mo!
